description.value:
For service to Northgate via downtown Seattle, from Seattle -Tacoma International Airport: 

On weekdays and Saturday, the last through train to Northgate Station with service to downtown Seattle departs SeaTac/Airport Station at about 11:44 p.m. 

On Sundays, the last through train to Northgate Station with service to downtown Seattle departs SeaTac/Airport Station at about 11:14 p.m. 

For service to Angle Lake via downtown Seattle, to Seattle -Tacoma International Airport: 

On weekdays and Saturday, the last train with service to SeaTac/Airport Station departs Northgate Station at about 12:28 a.m. 

On Sundays, the last train with service to SeaTac/Airport Station departs Northgate Station at about 11:28 p.m.
